Articles.Content: When i launch KSP, it says there's an incompatibility with a KSPAPI extensions mod, except I don't have the KSPAPI extensions mod. Is there any way to get rid of the startup message?

KSPAPI Extensions is a library that is bundled with other mods. So find the other mod that includes the outdated version, and either update that mod to its latest version (presuming one is present) or remove it.

To find the outdated versions, do a search for kspapiextensions.dll and check the properties to find the version number. (Right-click, properties, details).
